Encoding: UTF-8
Package: kinshipExtra
Version: 1.0-0
License: GPL (>= 2)
Title: Additional pedigree functions for the kinship2 package
Description: Routines to plot a pedigree using a one dimensional layout, which
    is useful in annotating the axis of another plot to show relationships.
    Also, an alternative plotting mechanism using ggplot2.
Author: Shiv Venkatasubrahmanyam <shiv@alum.mit.edu>
Maintainer: Shiv Venkatasubrahmanyam <shiv@alum.mit.edu>
Imports:
    kinship2 (>= 1.5.4),
    ggplot2 (>= 0.9.3),
    scales
LazyData: true
